06:21.640 --> 06:25.510
- Daddy's here.
- There were monsters.

06:25.540 --> 06:29.640
No, sweetie. There's
no such thing as monsters.

06:29.680 --> 06:31.380
You were just having
a bad dream.

06:31.420 --> 06:32.580
What's wrong, Dad?

06:34.450 --> 06:38.180
Hi, kiddo.
Sarah's just having a bad dream.

06:38.220 --> 06:39.990
Oh.

06:40.030 --> 06:42.120
I saw monsters, Jack.

06:42.160 --> 06:43.990
Monsters?

06:44.030 --> 06:45.720
What kind?

06:45.770 --> 06:48.100
I don't know.
They came out of my closet...

06:48.130 --> 06:49.690
and then
they were in the shadows.

06:49.740 --> 06:52.640
Mmm, shadow monsters.

06:52.670 --> 06:53.800
Well, they look pretty scary...

06:53.840 --> 06:55.470
but they really
can't do anything...

06:55.510 --> 06:57.140
especially
when the lights are on.

06:57.180 --> 06:58.800
They're scared of the light.

06:58.840 --> 07:00.810
What happened, baby?

07:01.950 --> 07:04.110
- You OK?
- I'm OK.

07:04.150 --> 07:06.050
Sarah had a bad dream
about monsters.

07:06.090 --> 07:08.210
- Oh.
- And I was telling her...

07:08.250 --> 07:10.090
that there's
no such thing as monsters.

07:10.120 --> 07:11.490
Oh.

07:11.520 --> 07:14.190
I'm going to turn on
my night light just in case.

07:14.230 --> 07:16.720
That sounds like
a brilliant solution.

07:18.130 --> 07:19.460
Mmm.

07:23.940 --> 07:26.840
- Hey, Jack?
- Hey, Mom?

07:26.870 --> 07:29.400
Morning.

07:29.440 --> 07:31.000
Morning, baby.

07:33.680 --> 07:36.240
Hey, hon,
the pick up still won't start.

07:36.280 --> 07:37.340
You mind dropping me off
on the way in?

07:37.380 --> 07:38.480
Sure.

07:41.520 --> 07:44.150
- Did you feed Burrow?
- Yeah, I fed him.

07:44.190 --> 07:46.520
All right. Good.

07:46.560 --> 07:48.550
The night light worked,
didn't it?

07:52.630 --> 07:54.530
I got it, Dad.

08:00.470 --> 08:03.410
What do you got going today,
Jack?

08:03.440 --> 08:05.740
Uh, nothing much.
A math test in a few days...

08:05.780 --> 08:09.180
and I think we're playing
baseball in gym class today...

08:09.220 --> 08:12.280
so I can look forward
to sucking hard in right field.

08:12.320 --> 08:13.910
Well, just remember...

08:15.290 --> 08:16.780
don't let the hitter
get the ball over your head...

08:16.820 --> 08:19.420
Unless it's out of the park.

08:19.460 --> 08:22.450
Well, yeah.

08:46.820 --> 08:48.340
Bye.

08:51.020 --> 08:52.650
I get off early today.
All I have...

08:52.690 --> 08:55.390
